Package: GanaderiaSostenible
Title: Carbon Capture and Biodiversity Estimations for Colombian Farms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Juan Pablo",
           family = "Marin Diaz",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jpmarindiaz@gmail.com")
Description: Provides an interface to calculate carbon capture in Colombia and 
    estimations of bird biodiversity for given regions and land coverage types.
    The package includes a web shiny app for non-tech end users to provide the
    area numbers of land coverage types of their farms (forests, pastures, etc)
    and the tool returns carbon captures and bird species estimates in Colombia, 
    available also as functions with a 20 year span for estimations.
